<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span style="color:#006d98">وَالمَفْعُولُ الثَّانِي:</span> <span style="color:#008000">(مُغْلَقَةً)</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>المَفْعُولُ المُطْلَقُ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span style="color:#006d98">وَالمَفْعُولُ المُطْلَقُ:</span> اسْمٌ لِتَأْكِيدِ الفِعْلِ أَوْ بَيَانِ نَوْعِهِ أَوْ عَدَدِهِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span style="color:#006d98">وَهُوَ:</span> مَنْصُوبٌ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>١ -<span style="color:#006d98"> فَمِثَالُ التَّوْكِيدِ:</span> <span style="color:#008000">(أَكْلًا)</span> فِي: <span style="color:#008000">(أَكَلَ الوَلَدُ أَكْلًا)</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>٢ -<span style="color:#006d98"> وَمِثَالُ بَيَانِ النَّوْعِ:</span> <span style="color:#008000">(جَرْيَ)</span> فِي: <span style="color:#008000">(جَرَى الوَلَدُ جَرْيَ الفَهْدِ)</span>.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>٣ -<span style="color:#006d98"> وَمِثَالُ العَدَدِ:</span> <span style="color:#008000">(أَكْلَتَيْنِ)</span>: فِي: <span style="color:#008000">(أَكَلَ الوَلَدُ أَكْلَتَيْنِ)</span>.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>وَيَقَعُ مَعْنَوِيًّا؛<span style="color:#006d98"> مِثْلُ:</span> <span style="color:#008000">(جَلَسْتُ قُعُودًا)</span>، وَ <span style="color:#008000">(قُمْتُ وُقُوفًا)</span>.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>المَفْعُولُ لِأَجْلِهِ <span style="color:#008000">(أَوْ لَهُ)</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span style="color:#006d98">وَالمَفْعُولُ لِأَجْلِهِ:</span> اسْمٌ يُبَيِّنُ سَبَبَ الفِعْلِ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span style="color:#006d98">وَهُوَ:</span> مَنْصُوبٌ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span style="color:#006d98">مِثَالُهُ:</span> <span style="color:#008000">(سَافَرَ زَيْدٌ طَلَبًا لِلرِّزْقِ)</span>.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span style="color:#006d98">فَالمَفْعُولُ لِأَجْلِهِ:</span> <span style="color:#008000">(طَلَبًا)</span>.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>المَفْعُولُ فِيهِ <span style="color:#008000">(ظَرْفُ الزَّمَانِ وَالمَكَانِ)</span><a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span style="color:#006d98">وَالظَّرْفُ:</span> اسْمٌ يُبَيِّنُ الزَّمَانَ أَوِ المَكَانَ الَّذِي حَصَلَ فِيهِ الفِعْلُ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span style="color:#006d98">وَهُوَ:</span> مَنْصُوبٌ إِذَا جَاءَ فِي مَوْضِعِهِ ظَرْفًا.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span><span style="color:#006d98">فَمِنْ ظُرُوفِ الزَّمَانِ:</span> <span style="color:#008000">(اليَوْمَ، وَاللَّيْلَةَ، وَالسَّاعَةَ، وَالشَّهْرَ، وَالسَّنَةَ، وَقَبْلَ، وَبَعْدَ، وَصَبَاحًا، وَمَسَاءً، وَغَدًا)</span>.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span><span style="color:#006d98">وَمِنْ ظُرُوفِ المَكَانِ:</span> <span style="color:#008000">(خَلْفَ، وَأَمَامَ، وَفَوْقَ، وَتَحْتَ، وَعِنْدَ، وَحَوْلَ)</span>.<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span><span style="color:#006d98">فَمَثِالُ ظَرْفِ الزَّمَانِ:</span> <span style="color:#008000">(سَيُسَافِرُ زَيْدٌ اللَّيْلَةَ)</span>.<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>فَـ <span style="color:#008000">(اللَّيْلَةَ)</span>: ظَرْفُ زَمَانٍ.<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span><span style="color:#006d98">وَمِثَالُ ظَرْفِ المَكَانِ:</span> <span style="color:#008000">(جَلَسْتُ أَمَامَ زَيْدٍ)</span>.<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span>فَـ <span style="color:#008000">(أَمَامَ)</span>: ظَرْفُ مَكَانٍ.<a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>